### Create Organization (Super Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/organizations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "New Corporation",
  "email": "info@newcorp.com",
  "tax_id": "987654321",
  "legal_name": "New Corporation Ltd",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "website": "https://newcorp.com",
  "state": "active"
}

### Update Organization
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/organizations/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Corporation Name",
  "website": "https://updatedcorp.com"
}

### Delete Organization (Super Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/organizations/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}
